title: Car Gauge Pro (OBD2 + Enhance) v3.66.26 (CTRC)
description:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/Q4wmXNb.png[/img]

[b]Requirements:[/b] 2.0 and up

[b]Overview:[/b] A complete OBD2 Generic package for all of the OBD2 compliant vehicles and with Enhanced Diagnostic Data for your GM, Ford, Toyota, KIA and Nissan. One of the most powerful and comprehensive scan tool app in the Android Market!
A complete OBD2 Generic package for all of the OBD2 compliant vehicles and with Enhanced Diagnostic Data for your GM, Ford, Toyota, KIA and Nissan. One of the most powerful and comprehensive scan tool app in the Android Market!

The application will communicate with the vehicle computers at the 16 Pin OBD2 diagnostic connector. Most of the OBD2 connector location should be under the Steering Wheel Compartment. Elm 327 or STN Bluetooth device is required to make this application work. Car Gauge Pro not only can be exciting with gauges, it is a professional scan tool. Do you have a check engine light on? Do you want to know the Readiness Status will pass for a Smog Inspection? Do you want to check the functionality of the sensors and determine the status of the Mode 5/6 Emission On-board Test? Car Gauge Pro will show you.
[b]
